#{{note|Megens}} M. Megens, J. Aizenberg, Nature 242, 1014 (2003), see {{cite web|url= http://www.deas.harvard.edu/brenner/Like_charged_particles.pdf |title=Harvard }}&nbsp;{{small|(61.0&nbsp;KB)}}
